  "remarks": "Member of the Rajah Solaiman Movement (QDe.128). Father's name is\nFeliciano Delos Reyes Sr. Mother's name is Aurea Semborio. In detention in the\nPhilippines as of May 2011. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008)\nwas concluded on 13 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
